find the moving average 3days(yesterday, today and tomorrow)
id   date       sales
1	  2021-01-01	52
2	  2021-01-02	63
3	  2021-01-03	54
4 	2021-01-04	76
5	  2021-01-05	66
6	  2021-01-06	86
7	  2021-01-07	76
8	  2021-01-08	96
9	  2021-01-09	36
10	2021-01-10	48
11	2021-01-11	69
12	2021-01-12	58
13	2021-01-13	98




__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________-
select *, avg(sales) over(order by Date rows between 2 preceding and current row) as three_day_moving_avg
from dataset;

________________________________________________________________________________________________________-
find the moving average 10days(previous 9 days and current day):-

select *, avg(sales) over(order by Date rows between 9 preceding and current row) as three_day_moving_avg
from dataset;




__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________-

find the moving average 30days(previous 29 days and current day):-
select *, avg(sales) over(order by Date rows between 29 preceding and current row) as three_day_moving_avg
from dataset;


